# Normalize all text files to LF in the index; working trees follow
# core.autocrlf / platform settings. The index was verified all-LF on
# 2026-06-11 (git ls-files --eol: zero i/crlf, zero i/mixed) — this pins
# that convention repo-side so clones with other local configs can't
# commit CRLF into history.
* text=auto

# Unambiguous binaries — auto-detection catches these anyway; explicit
# for documentation.
*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.webp binary
*.ttf binary
*.otf binary
